Deputy President William Ruto's remarks last week, hinting at a likely political alliance with ODM party leader Raila Odinga has got tongues wagging. KTN senior political reporter Murimi Mwangi revisits previous Ruto-Raila alliances and explains why the duo&rsquo;s allies fear there may be an all-out scheme by the state to neutralize traditional Ruto -Raila political constituencies ahead of the 2022 election.